    "code": "A-RG-3",
    "trait": "Agreeableness",
    "facet": "Respect for Guidance",
    "facetId": "A-RG",
    "text": "I get annoyed when people give me health tips, even if they mean well.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 65,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "A-CP-1",
    "code": "A-CP-1",
    "trait": "Agreeableness",
    "facet": "Cooperative Participation",
    "facetId": "A-CP",
    "text": "I find it more enjoyable to work on fitness goals when I have a partner or group to do it with.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 66,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "A-CP-2",
    "code": "A-CP-2",
    "trait": "Agreeableness",
    "facet": "Cooperative Participation",
    "facetId": "A-CP",
    "text": "If my workout partner needs to go slower or faster, I'm happy to match their pace.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 67,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "A-CP-3",
    "code": "A-CP-3",
    "trait": "Agreeableness",
    "facet": "Cooperative Participation",
    "facetId": "A-CP",
    "text": "Even when exercising with others, I like to follow my own plan rather than the group's.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 68,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "A-SR-1",
    "code": "A-SR-1",
    "trait": "Agreeableness",
    "facet": "Shared Recovery Respect",
    "facetId": "A-SR",
    "text": "If someone at home is resting, I try to keep the noise down and avoid disturbing them.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 69,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "A-SR-2",
    "code": "A-SR-2",
    "trait": "Agreeableness",
    "facet": "Shared Recovery Respect",
    "facetId": "A-SR",
    "text": "When a friend, family member or colleague says they need rest after a tiring day, I avoid asking them to do things until they've recovered.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 70,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "A-SR-3",
    "code": "A-SR-3",
    "trait": "Agreeableness",
    "facet": "Shared Recovery Respect",
    "facetId": "A-SR",
    "text": "I often do my own thing without checking if it might disturb someone who is trying to rest.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 71,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-HA-1",
    "code": "N-HA-1",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Health Anxiety Sensitivity",
    "facetId": "N-HA",
    "text": "I quickly worry when I notice small changes in how my body feels.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 72,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-HA-2",
    "code": "N-HA-2",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Health Anxiety Sensitivity",
    "facetId": "N-HA",
    "text": "Reading about health issues or symptoms online often leaves me feeling worried.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 73,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-HA-3",
    "code": "N-HA-3",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Health Anxiety Sensitivity",
    "facetId": "N-HA",
    "text": "When I notice a small ache or unusual feeling in my body, I don't jump to conclusions and worry about it.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 74,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-EE-1",
    "code": "N-EE-1",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Emotional Eating Response",
    "facetId": "N-EE",
    "text": "When I'm feeling low, I often reach for food to feel better.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 75,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-EE-2",
    "code": "N-EE-2",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Emotional Eating Response",
    "facetId": "N-EE",
    "text": "On stressful days, I tend to eat more than usual or skip meals entirely.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 76,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-EE-3",
    "code": "N-EE-3",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Emotional Eating Response",
    "facetId": "N-EE",
    "text": "Whether I'm happy or upset, I usually eat the same kinds of foods.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 77,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-SC-1",
    "code": "N-SC-1",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Stress Impact on Consistency",
    "facetId": "N-SC",
    "text": "When life gets stressful, wellness becomes less important to me than other things.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 78,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-SC-2",
    "code": "N-SC-2",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Stress Impact on Consistency",
    "facetId": "N-SC",
    "text": "During stressful times, I lose the motivation to take care of my health.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 79,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-SC-3",
    "code": "N-SC-3",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Stress Impact on Consistency",
    "facetId": "N-SC",
    "text": "I can usually keep basic wellness habits going even when life feels stressful.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 80,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-SW-1",
    "code": "N-SW-1",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Sleep Worry & Mental Overload",
    "facetId": "N-SW",
    "text": "Worrying thoughts often make it hard for me to sleep at night.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 81,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-SW-2",
    "code": "N-SW-2",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Sleep Worry & Mental Overload",
    "facetId": "N-SW",
    "text": "After a mentally tiring day, I find it hard to switch off and fall asleep.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 82,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-SW-3",
    "code": "N-SW-3",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Sleep Worry & Mental Overload",
    "facetId": "N-SW",
    "text": "During stressful periods, I can usually calm my mind enough to rest when I need to.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 83,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-WS-1",
    "code": "N-WS-1",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Wellness Stability",
    "facetId": "N-WS",
    "text": "I sometimes go from eating perfectly and exercising daily to completely letting go for days.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 84,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-WS-2",
    "code": "N-WS-2",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Wellness Stability",
    "facetId": "N-WS",
    "text": "One bad day can make me feel like my whole wellness routine has gone off track.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 85,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-WS-3",
    "code": "N-WS-3",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Wellness Stability",
    "facetId": "N-WS",
    "text": "My approach to wellness usually stays balanced even after a setback.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 86,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-ER-1",
    "code": "N-ER-1",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Emotional Recovery Resilience",
    "facetId": "N-ER",
    "text": "After missing a workout or eating poorly, it takes me a while to stop feeling bad about it.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 87,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-ER-2",
    "code": "N-ER-2",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Emotional Recovery Resilience",
    "facetId": "N-ER",
    "text": "When I skip a healthy routine I meant to follow, I tend to be hard on myself.",
    "is_reverse": false,
    "order_index": 88,
    "is_active": true
  },
  {
    "id": "N-ER-3",
    "code": "N-ER-3",
    "trait": "Neuroticism",
    "facet": "Emotional Recovery Resilience",
    "facetId": "N-ER",
    "text": "After a bad day, I usually bounce back and get going again without much trouble.",
    "is_reverse": true,
    "order_index": 89,
    "is_active": true
  }
]